---
import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro";
import Header from "../components/Header.astro";
import Footer from "../components/Footer.astro";
---

<Layout title="About | Creativ Audio" description="Learn about Creativ Audio, built by a music producer and developer with over 12 years of experience to empower creativity in modern production.">
  <Header />
  <main>
    <!-- Hero -->
    <section class="flex flex-col items-center gap-6 pt-20 md:pt-32 pb-16 md:pb-24 px-6 md:px-16 lg:px-20">
      <span class="text-xs font-semibold text-accent tracking-[2px] uppercase">About Us</span>
      <h1 class="font-heading text-4xl md:text-[56px] font-bold text-text-primary tracking-[-1px] text-center leading-tight max-w-[700px]">
        Built by a Producer,<br />for Producers
      </h1>
      <p class="text-base md:text-lg text-text-body text-center max-w-[560px] leading-relaxed">
        Creativ Audio is an independently owned audio software company on a mission to build tools that unlock creativity and streamline the production workflow.
      </p>
    </section>

    <!-- Divider -->
    <div class="w-full h-px bg-border"></div>

    <!-- Story -->
    <section class="flex flex-col items-center py-16 md:py-24 px-6 md:px-16 lg:px-20">
      <div class="max-w-[680px] flex flex-col gap-8 text-[15px] text-text-body leading-relaxed">
        <h2 class="font-heading text-2xl md:text-3xl font-bold text-text-primary">The Story Behind Creativ Audio</h2>
        <p>
          Creativ Audio was founded by <strong class="text-text-primary">Qosmar</strong>, a music producer and software developer from Spain with over 12 years of experience in music production and audio development. What started as a personal quest to solve real problems in the studio eventually grew into something bigger: a company dedicated to building the tools that producers actually need.
        </p>
        <p>
          After years of producing, mixing, and experimenting with countless plugins, one thing became clear: there was a gap between what producers wanted and what was available. Too many tools prioritized complexity over creativity. Too many workflows felt slow and unintuitive. Creativ Audio was born out of the desire to change that.
        </p>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Divider -->
    <div class="w-full h-px bg-border"></div>

    <!-- Mission -->
    <section class="flex flex-col items-center py-16 md:py-24 px-6 md:px-16 lg:px-20">
      <div class="max-w-[680px] flex flex-col gap-8 text-[15px] text-text-body leading-relaxed">
        <h2 class="font-heading text-2xl md:text-3xl font-bold text-text-primary">Our Mission</h2>
        <p>
          We believe that great music comes from great ideas, not from fighting your tools. Every plugin we build is designed with two goals in mind: <strong class="text-text-primary">spark creativity</strong> and <strong class="text-text-primary">simplify the workflow</strong>.
        </p>
        <p>
          Whether you're a bedroom producer sketching out your first beat or a seasoned engineer polishing a final mix, our tools are made to get out of your way and let you focus on what matters: the music.
        </p>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Divider -->
    <div class="w-full h-px bg-border"></div>

    <!-- Values -->
    <section class="flex flex-col items-center py-16 md:py-24 px-6 md:px-16 lg:px-20">
      <div class="max-w-[680px] flex flex-col gap-10">
        <h2 class="font-heading text-2xl md:text-3xl font-bold text-text-primary">What We Stand For</h2>
        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-8">
          <div class="flex flex-col gap-3">
            <h3 class="text-base font-semibold text-text-primary">Producer-First Design</h3>
            <p class="text-[15px] text-text-body leading-relaxed">Every feature is born from real production needs. We build what we wish existed in our own sessions.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="flex flex-col gap-3">
            <h3 class="text-base font-semibold text-text-primary">Creativity Over Complexity</h3>
            <p class="text-[15px] text-text-body leading-relaxed">Powerful under the hood, intuitive on the surface. Our plugins inspire ideas without overwhelming you.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="flex flex-col gap-3">
            <h3 class="text-base font-semibold text-text-primary">Independent & Passionate</h3>
            <p class="text-[15px] text-text-body leading-relaxed">We're not backed by a corporation. We're a small team driven by a genuine love for music and technology.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="flex flex-col gap-3">
            <h3 class="text-base font-semibold text-text-primary">Built for the Community</h3>
            <p class="text-[15px] text-text-body leading-relaxed">We listen to producers, iterate based on real feedback, and grow alongside the people who use our tools.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Divider -->
    <div class="w-full h-px bg-border"></div>

    <!-- CTA -->
    <section class="flex flex-col items-center gap-6 py-16 md:py-24 px-6 md:px-16 lg:px-20">
      <h2 class="font-heading text-2xl md:text-3xl font-bold text-text-primary text-center">Ready to Elevate Your Sound?</h2>
      <p class="text-base text-text-body text-center max-w-[480px]">Explore our plugins and see how Creativ Audio can transform your production workflow.</p>
      <a
        href="/#pricing"
        class="rounded-md bg-gradient-to-r from-accent to-accent-end px-10 py-4 text-[14px] font-semibold text-white tracking-[0.5px] hover:opacity-90 transition-opacity mt-2"
      >
        Discover Our Products
      </a>
    </section>
  </main>
  <Footer />
</Layout>
